                            <comment id="12627163" author="hossman" created="Sat, 30 Aug 2008 00:56:51 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;1) I&apos;m an idiot.  that first log message clearly indicates that that is a list of &quot;hidden&quot; files, so it&apos;s not suppose to match what&apos;s in gettableFiles.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;2) &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-493&quot; title=&quot;/admin/file links don&amp;#39;t work with legacy configs&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SOLR-493&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SOLR-493&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; was the issue that i thought fixed this ... looking over that patch in more detail the problem seems to be that the automatically created instance of ShowFileRequestHandler is registered with the name &quot;admin/file&quot; ... note the missing leading slash.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;quick testing seems to indicate that adding the slash fixes the problem ... running full test suite now, will commit to 1.3 and trunk once i&apos;m sure it&apos;s working.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
